    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows clear signs of its age, including some visible exterior scratches, minor paint fading, and interior wear on the upholstery. There are a few small mechanical items that may require attention in the near future, such as a slow window motor and a minor oil weep. It has been a dependable driver for us, but it is no longer in the 'good' condition it once was, and we have priced it accordingly to reflect its current state.",
